{"tid":2127602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Live] 立法會區議會（一 ） 網上選舉論壇 有8位區議員出席","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:46:30.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"349831cf7722d6172628ec7410c0575757892c8e","tid":2127602,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"【區議會(一)功能界別 選舉論壇】<br />\n幾經波折，今晚最後將可舉行區一論壇，方便市民及區議員認識有意參選人士，以下是詳情：<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月27日(今晚)<br />\n時間：20：00～22：00<br />\n主持：葉錦龍 張文龍<br />\n<br />\n大家屆時可透過 梁柏堅（表弟） Pakkin Leung 葉錦龍　Sam Yip 及 張文龍 Dennis Cheung 面書專頁觀看。<br />\n<br />\n今次論壇參加者有(排名不分先後)：<br />\n1. 任啟邦 （大埔）<br />\n2. 李家偉 （屯門）<br />\n3. 陳振哲 （大埔）<br />\n4. 司馬文 （南區）<br />\n5. 仇栩欣 （東區）<br />\n6. 劉卓裕 （荃灣）<br />\n7. 莫灝哲 （黃大仙）<br />\n8. 麥德正 （東區）<br />\n<br />\n另外大會亦有邀請劉佩玉（深水埗），但大會未有收到其任何回應，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/283320649660388/?vh=e&amp;extid=EBc4p1f62e2gpnjC&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F283320649660388%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DEBc4p1f62e2gpnjC%26d%3Dn&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=cbba830d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/283320649660388/?vh=e&amp;extid=EBc4p1f62e2gpnjC&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7e2c34e3e9a6eec0c0f5a982e74036e4e4c14c25","tid":2127602,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b1023e11ea87e71ce7cd401712fde657f041ba","tid":2127602,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"要傳譯?"},{"pid":"decce6649df0e43aad57540dac6a0e4b29a71415","tid":2127602,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2c34e3e9a6eec0c0f5a982e74036e4e4c14c25","tid":2127602,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim